      <h1
        class="font-extralight text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl md:max-w-xl md:leading-[4rem] xl:text-6xl xl:max-w-3xl xl:leading-[5rem]"
      >
        We Have A Goal To Achieve You To Your Destination
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section> -->

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="py-0">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center min-[991px]:flex-row"
      >
        <div
          class="min-[991px]:min-w-[400px] px-4 min-[991px]:px-5 min-[991px]:pr-0"
        >
          <Image
            src={img1}
            class="object-cover w-full md:max-w-[550px] xl:max-w-[650px]"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10 min-[991px]:mb-5 w-full min-[991px]:w-fit">
          <div
            class="relative isolate self-end flex flex-col gap-2 z-[1] p-4 lg:pl-6 xl:pl-8"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 z-[-1] h-[80%] top-[21.1%] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_farthest-corner_at_10%_20%,rgba(176,229,208,1)_42%,rgba(92,202,238,0.41)_93.6%)] min-[991px]:right-[-100%] shadow-inner"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="">
              <!-- <span
                class="text-[2px] md:text-base pb-1 leading-[0] font-bold text-fuchsia-900"
              >
                .
              </span> -->
              <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl md:text-[45px] lg:text-6xl text-indigo-900 max-w-[510px] lg:max-w-[700px] font-extrabold"
              >
                About
                <b class="font-medium italic text-indigo-800"
                  >Gajinkar Builders</b
                >
              </h2>
              <h3
                class="text-xl text-indigo-800 max-w-[510px] lg:max-w-[700px] font-bold p-2"
              >
                Crafting Excellence in Construction Since 1995:
              </h3>
              <p
                class="max-w-[520px] px-2 text-neutral-700 text-sm font-medium mb-0 md:text-base"
              >
                Founded by Santosh Gajinkar, Gajinkar Builders is a symbol of
                construction excellence with a legacy spanning 27 years. Our
                dedicated team blends visionary leadership with an unwavering
                commitment to quality, transforming your dreams into timeless
                realities. Since our inception in 1995, we've been steadfast in
                crafting spaces that surpass expectations.
              </p>
              <h3
                class="text-xl text-indigo-800 max-w-[510px] lg:max-w-[700px] font-bold p-2"
              >
                Diverse Ventures:
              </h3>
              <p
                class="max-w-[520px] px-2 text-neutral-700 text-sm font-medium mb-0 md:text-base"
              >
                In addition to our construction endeavors, we proudly own a
                tennis academy in Pundaliknagar, Porvorim, contributing to
                sports development and community engagement. This diversified
                approach reflects our commitment to both quality construction
                and enriching community experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 mb-5">
              <h3 class="text-xl text-fuchsia-900 font-bold">
                Our Headquarters:
                <span class="text-lg text-teal-800 font-semibold"
                  >Betim, Bardez - Goa</span
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mission-vision-section">
    <div class="p-4 py-4 flex justify-center items-center">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center lg:max-w-5xl xl:max-w-6xl 2xl:max-w-[1400px]"
      >
        <div class="md:px-2">
          <h2 class="uppercase text-sm text-indigo-900 font-medium">
            Our Mission & Vision
          </h2>

          <div
            class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center py-3"
          >
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-2 xl:text-4xl">
                Mission
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 font-normal xl:text-base">
                Providing reliable and affordable housing with a commitment to
                exceptional quality in every endeavor.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3
                class="font-medium text-2xl md:text-3xl py-2 md:pt-2 xl:text-4xl"
              >
                Vision
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 font-normal xl:text-base">
                To expand ambitiously into the hospitality and sports
                industries, aiming for substantial growth and impact.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/aboutsection.png" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-goals rounded-t-3xl">
    <div class="p-4 py-6 lg:py-8">
      <h2
        class="text-center font-black text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl"
      >
        Projects
      </h2>
      <h3
        class="text-xl my-2 mt-4 md:my-4 md:mt-6 lg:my-6 lg:mt-8 text-center font-semibold text-white py-2 bg-[#00000061] shadow-inner rounded-lg md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl md:py-3 lg:py-5 2xl:py-6 xl:text-4xl"
      >
        Crafting Excellence in Construction - A Legacy Built
      </h3>
      <div
        class="p-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row text-white gap-2 md:gap-4 lg:gap-6 xl:gap-8 2xl:gap-10 justify-center items-center md:text-lg lg:text-xl"
      >
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-[#00000071] md:max-w-[400px] border-2 border-fuchsia-500"
        >
          <Image src={img1} alt="" class="h-[20vh] object-cover lg:h-[30vh]" />
          <div class="p-2 flex justify-between items-center">
            <h2>Completed Projects - 6</h2>
            <a
              href="/completed-projects"
              class="m-1 inline-block bg-indigo-600 p-2 rounded-3xl px-3"
              >View All</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-[#00000071] md:max-w-[400px] border-2 border-fuchsia-500"
        >
          <Image src={img1} alt="" class="h-[20vh] object-cover lg:h-[30vh]" />
          <div class="p-2 flex justify-between items-center">
            <h2>On - Going Projects - 2</h2>
            <a
              href="/ongoing-projects"
              class="m-1 inline-block bg-indigo-600 p-2 rounded-3xl px-3"
              >View All</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="py-8 bg-fuchsia-200">
      <h2
        class="text-center font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl"
      >
        What Sets Gajinkar Builders Apart?
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center gap-3 p-4 md:gap-6 md:p-8 xl:gap-8 xl:p-10 lg:max-w-[1100px]"
      >
        <div
          class="border-2 border-fuchsia-600 rounded-md p-2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow h-full lg:p-4"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl">Legacy of Excellence</h3>
          <p class="font-medium pt-2 text-base lg:text-lg">
            We bring a wealth of experience and a proven track record of
            construction excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-2 border-fuchsia-600 rounded-md p-2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow h-full lg:p-4"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl">Visionary Leadership</h3>
          <p class="font-medium pt-2 text-base lg:text-lg">
            Our team is guided by visionary leadership committed to pushing the
            boundaries of quality construction.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-2 border-fuchsia-600 rounded-md p-2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow h-full lg:p-4"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl">Commitment to Quality</h3>
          <p class="font-medium pt-2 text-base lg:text-lg">
            Our unwavering commitment to quality ensures that every project
            transforms dreams into enduring realities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-2 border-fuchsia-600 rounded-md p-2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center transition-all duration-700 shadow-xl hover:shadow h-full lg:p-4"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl">Community Engagement</h3>
          <p class="font-medium pt-2 text-base lg:text-lg">
            Beyond construction, we proudly own a tennis academy in
            Pundaliknagar, Porvorim, contributing to sports development and
            community enrichment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 via-gray-950 to-black rounded-t-3xl"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-center text-2xl p-2 py-6 text-white capitalize md:py-8 md:text-3xl font-semibold xl:text-4xl xl:py-10"
    >
      Where excellence is not just a goal; it's our legacy.
    </h2>
  </section>

  <MapSection />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background-image: url("/images/abouthero.jpg");
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .about-bg1 {
    background-image: url("/images/projects.png");
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .about-goals {
    background-image: linear-gradient(
      111.4deg,
      rgba(7, 7, 9, 1) 6.5%,
      rgba(27, 24, 113, 1) 93.2%
    );
  }
</style>
